-- Environmental Curbs on Coal India Mining Reserves Lifted, Express Reports
-- B y   N a t a l i e   O b i k o   P e a r s o n
-- 2010-10-16T04:41:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-16/environmental-curbs-on-coal-india-mining-reserves-lifted-express-reports.html
Indian Prime Minister Manmohan
Singh’s office stopped a plan by the environment ministry
prohibiting Coal India Ltd. from mining 40 percent of its
reserves, the Financial Express newspaper said, citing an
official it didn’t identify.   Click here for web link  To contact the reporter on this story:
